{"tid":1533370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明天罷工罷課既手足不如圍狗鐵要求交代831太子事件同交出cctv","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:28:09.000Z","uid":262297,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef32f6d3ae281ccf77f0362d9cddb54bc1666f2b","tid":1533370,"uid":262297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"而家手足生死未卜，班3毛又係咁亂放d假消息出黎俾人一check就知假既<br />\n我唔知佢地係咪想等大家覺得死人係假，而轉移大家視線幫d狗淡化831打死人事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡簡單單，而家班黑狗同狗鐵話無打死人，就唔該佢地提供返無死人既證據出黎，如果交唔撚到我話知你點講，我點都會話你班仆街有打死人<br />\n<br />\n如果真係打死左人，而成個警隊連各級高官一齊合謀隱暪事實，咁呢個所謂法治既社會已經俾呢班人完全毀滅晒，香港唔會再有法治呢樣野啦<br />\n<br />\n到時召喚仲有良知既市民一齊上街聽討黑警，並宣佈唔撚再承認班黑狗係合法既警察"},{"pid":"26079c86774729aae8410b7adab385fda7130973","tid":1533370,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"popo進化到 少林寺十八銅人跳舞方法<br />\n震精750萬港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChinaziSS/status/1168551744885837825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChinaziSS%2Fstatus%2F1168551744885837825&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=90c863e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChinaziSS%2Fstatus%2F1168551744885837825&h=69284a9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ChinaziSS/status/1168551744885837825</a>"},{"pid":"95273b7020cc73d7cfcb99827525b85c51a02e5a","tid":1533370,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:07:22.000Z","msg":"fb有消息了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2470630179821344/permalink/2514051912145837?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2470630179821344%2Fpermalink%2F2514051912145837%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=63eb1535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2470630179821344/permalink/2514051912145837?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"7cbc5e6ad91a9e90805f9a879117daa05aacafa2","tid":1533370,"uid":262297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"求求大家呀，一齊幫忙呼籲大家圍狗鐵交代事件啦，唔可以真係俾手足死得不明不白<br />\n<br />\n你地諗下呀，一堆三毛係咁衝出黎係咁放假消息等大家炒車，然後大家無fc就唔會再信其他消息，但而家班狗封站成日，邊可能會fc到，唯一線索只有狗鐵手上既cctv<br />\n<br />\n今日 92班狗又大規模出動作亂，今日又唔係咩大班遊行，經過前2日得罪咁多市民，點解佢地唔收斂一下？係咪真係有咁既必要呢？會唔會係想藉由更多事件去掩蓋831既事呢？<br />\n<br />\n暫時真相係點無人知，如果我地唔去逼狗鐵交代，個事實就永遠無人知，但我寧願炒車都好，我都唔希望有手足白白犧牲，而個兇手同埋個殺人就政權逍遙法外"},{"pid":"7f91dfc26cf2a646ec5f0c72baeb2ccd277887fb","tid":1533370,"uid":262297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95273b7020cc73d7cfcb99827525b85c51a02e5a","tid":1533370,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:07:22.000Z","msg":"fb有消息了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2470630179821344/permalink/2514051912145837?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2470630179821344%2Fpermalink%2F2514051912145837%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=63eb1535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2470630179821344/permalink/2514051912145837?sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:26:40.000Z","msg":"唔會信呢d消息，係要狗鐵交代，否則雖然未有證據，但我會堅持佢地係打死人"},{"pid":"a0f95de9b16c5e5f22594d9bab7eb118fba40fe8","tid":1533370,"uid":262297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:38:14.000Z","msg":"唔信網上任何消息，但堅信黑狗打人，要求唯一真相，要求狗鐵交代封站一日入面發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n我知可能會有人覺得我想引大家去炒車，唔緊要！<br />\n<br />\n如果有人同我一樣諗法既，明天就一齊去九龍灣圍總部大樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec2702c589f01a42ee5d4c72c8b2cd41cb18b96","tid":1533370,"uid":208046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:26:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de6791565e51129ab52e